[{"id":"VR619216","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"passage\"><div class=\"prose style:1\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows two spheres along a horizontal axis at two different points in time. The sphere on the left has mass m, and the sphere on the right is labeled 4 m. Initially, the spheres are separated by an unspecified distance, then, the sphere on the left is moved a distance delta x to the right, and the sphere on the right is moved a distance delta x to the left.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR619216.g01.svg\"/></div></div></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Two spheres, with masses indicated in the figure, are initially at the positions on the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x\"><math alttext=\"x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>x</mi></math></span></span>-axis shown in the top figure. Each sphere is then moved a distance <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"delta x\"><math alttext=\"delta x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><mi>x</mi></math></span></span> toward the other, as shown in the bottom figure. Which of the following correctly indicates how the location of the center of mass of the two-sphere system changes between the top figure and the bottom figure?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR619216_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Moves to the left by an amount less than <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"delta x\"><math alttext=\"delta x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><mi>x</mi></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Moves to the left by an amount greater than <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"delta x\"><math alttext=\"delta x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><mi>x</mi></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Moves to the right by an amount less than <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"delta x\"><math alttext=\"delta x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><mi>x</mi></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Moves to the right by an amount greater than <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"delta x\"><math alttext=\"delta x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><mi>x</mi></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":0}]